Class IBNO055IMU.Velocity

  • java.lang.Object
    • IBNO055IMU.Velocity
  • Enclosing interface:
    IBNO055IMU

    public static class IBNO055IMU.Velocity
extends java.lang.Object
    Velocity represents a directed velocity in three-space. Units are as the same as for Accleration, but integrated for time.
